Configuration file reference:


public-block-details - show the block details to anyone (when right clicking on a pstone block), not just the owner
bypass-players - a list of players who will be able to bypass all protections
bypass-blocks - a list blocks types that anyone will be able to break or place inside force fields i.e. toches, etc..
unbreakable-blocks - list of block types that you want to be unbreakable
protection:
blocks - a block type that you want to radiate protection
radius - the radius of protection (radius of 2 would make a 5x5x5 field)
extra-height - extra veritcal height for the protected area
prevent fire - prevent players from starting fires in the protected area
prevent entry - prevent players from entering the protected area
prevent place - prevent players from placing blocks in a protected area
prevent destroy - prevent players from destroying blocks in the protected area
prevent explosions - prevent tnt and creeper explosions in the protected area
prevent pvp - prevent player damage inside the protected area
instant heal - heals any player that enters the protected area instantly
slow heal - heals any player in the protected area as they walk
slow damage - damages a player in the protected area as they walk
log:
place - log all pstone block placements
destroy - log all pstone block destructions
bypass-delete - log all field deletions by bypass players
bypass-destroy - log all pstone destruction by bypass players
notify:
place - notify the player when he places a pstone
destroy - notify the player when he destroys a pstone
bypass - notify the bypass player when he destroys a pstone
warn:
instant-heal - warn the player when he is instant healed by a protected area
slow-heal - warn the player when he is being slowly healed by a protected area
slow-damage - warn the player when he is slowly damaged by a protected area
fire - warn the player when he tries to start a fire on a fire-restricted protected area
entry - warn the player when he tries to enter an entry-restricted protected area
place - warn the player when he tries to pace a block on a place-restricted protected area
pvp - warn a player when he hits another that there is not pvp in the proteted area
destroy - warn a player when he tries to destroy a pstone that does not belong to him
destroy-area - warn the player when he tries to destroy a block inside a protected area

    
